aasai thambi ( english : dearest younger brother ) is a 1998 tamil drama film , written and directed by senthilnathan . the film stars arun pandian , abbas and anju aravind in the lead roles , while manivannan and ajay rathnam portray supporting roles . music for the film was composed by adithyan and the film opened to mixed reviews in september 1998 . this film is a remake of the 1989 hindi film parinda .